description:
This is a 32 minute workout called 'Standing Cardio Workout | No Jumping | Includes Warm Up and Cool Down Stretch | 30 Minutes' from the channel The Girl With The Pilates Mat.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Standing Cardio Workout | No Jumping | Includes Warm Up and Cool Down Stretch | 30 Minutes

Join me for a 30 minute standing pilates cardio workout. With a warm up, more intense exercises in the middle and lovely stretch to finish. This will raise your heart rate, burn fat, tone muscles and put a smile on your face as we move through low impact, high intensity and fun exercises to boost the metabolism and leave you feeling energised and raring to go. A great session to get going in the morning and I recommend you do this at least three times a week to see and feel the difference in your body. 

Do check out my other high energy workouts here:
